#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/managing_products/products.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Indication`: notifies if the price is **VAT included** or "
"**excluded**;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Indication taxes` : indique si le prix est **toutes taxes "
